      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BACKBEACH PETER (8) resumes from a spell of three-and-a-half months after closing off last campaign in good form, placing at Hamilton when last seen and winning twice in a row prior. Shouldn't spend a penny from this draw and with two trial wins under the belt he will be ready to run a big race to kick off this campaign. WEREGOINGTOGETCHA (10) won three back at this venue and registered another success last start, scoring by 2 metres at Port Pirie. Not drawn the best so may need a 10/10 drive but she is going well. MANDS PEARL (1) has been drawn on the back row in the last two outings but came from this barrier to win three back so is much better served here. KEAYANG HUNGRY (5) must be considered after he came from this barrier and finished third at Mt Gambier last start.",
